            <title>[HIVE-4521] Auto join conversion fails in certain cases (empty tables, empty partitions, no partitions)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-4521</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Automatic join conversion for both map joins as well as smb joins fails when tables, files or partitions are empty (see test cases in patch). Error messages include: &quot;Big Table Alias is null&quot; and &quot;Divide by Zero&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
